OL,3,CWoman faces eviction from family home
OL,4,Cafter parents' death
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's Mel Bloor
OL,7,Freports.
OL,9,FA grieving daughter has described
OL,10,FReading Borough Council as 'heartless'
OL,11,Fand 'ruthless', after being told
OL,12,Fshe'll be evicted from her home
OL,13,Ffollowing the death of her parents.
OL,15,FSharon Woodley and her husband moved
OL,16,Finto the council-owned property where
OL,17,Fshe grew up, to take care of her mum
OL,18,Fand dad in their final years.
