OL,3,CWoman faces eviction from family home
OL,4,Cafter parents' death
OL,6,FSharon's dad died in 2020 from
OL,7,Fpancreatic cancer while her mum, who
OL,8,Fhad dementia and Alzheimer's, died in
OL,9,FFebruary this year.
OL,11,FSpeaking with ITV News Meridian, they
OL,12,Ftold us they now face being made
OL,13,Fhomeless, after they were told the
OL,14,Fcouncil tenancy cannot be passed on to
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,FSharon said: "It was absolutely a
OL,18,Fmassive shock. We've made this like it
OL,19,Fwas mum and dad's home before, and
OL,20,Fwe've made it even more our home as
OL,21,Fwell.
