OL,6,F"I don't want to go anywhere else.
OL,7,FI've been here since I was 15 years
OL,8,Fold. I don't want to go anywhere else.
OL,9,FI've got all the memories of my mum
OL,10,Fand dad here, and we want to stay
OL,11,Fliving here."
OL,13,FSharon Woodley tells ITV Meridian
OL,14,Fabout how losing the home will be
OL,15,Fdevastating.
OL,17,FThe mid-terrace in South Reading is
OL,18,Fwhere Sharon Woodley and her husband
OL,19,FSimon have called home since 2017.
