OL,3,CWoman faces eviction from family home
OL,4,Cafter parents' death
OL,6,FFollowing Sharon's dad's death in
OL,7,F2020, the council tenancy, which was
OL,8,Foriginally in his name, was
OL,9,Fautomatically passed on to her mum.
OL,11,FAnd as there can only be one
OL,12,Fsuccession to a council tenancy, it
OL,13,Fnow can't be passed onto them.
OL,15,FBut the couple say Sharon's mum had
OL,16,Fdementia at the time of her dad's
OL,17,Fdeath and lacked the mental capacity
OL,18,Fto take on any agreement.
