OL,6,FSimon said: "Mum and Dad are still
OL,7,Fhere, we feel them. And that's what's
OL,8,Fupsetting, isn't it?
OL,10,F"The laws and regulations and what's
OL,11,Fhappened, we don't believe is correct,
OL,12,Fbasically.
OL,14,F"That succession should never have
OL,15,Ftaken place."
OL,17,FThe couple say they will fight the
OL,18,Feviction, even if that fight ends up
OL,19,Fin court.
