OL,3,CWoman faces eviction from family home
OL,4,Cafter parents' death
OL,6,FSimon Woodley told us he believes the
OL,7,Fcouncil hasn't followed its own rules.
OL,9,FIn a statement, a spokesperson from
OL,10,FReading Borough Council said:"We fully
OL,11,Fappreciate why this scenario is
OL,12,Fupsetting for families, particularly
OL,13,Fwhere a Council property has been the
OL,14,Ffamily home over many years.
OL,16,F"By law, only one succession to the
OL,17,Ftenancy is permitted (Housing Act
OL,18,F1985). In this instance, the
OL,19,Fsuccession passed from husband to wife
OL,20,Fwhen the tenant passed away in 2020.
