OL,6,F"Because Mrs Hayward was an occupant
OL,7,Fat the time of death, the criteria for
OL,8,Fsuccession was fulfilled, no formal
OL,9,Fsigning of documents was required at
OL,10,Fthe time and Mrs Hayward was able to
OL,11,Fsucceed her husband as tenant
OL,12,Fregardless of capacity.
OL,14,F"The Council has however explained the
OL,15,Fprocess to Mr Woodley and Ms North on
OL,16,Fseveral occasions, and as far back as
OL,17,FJune 2021.
