OL,6,F"We were very sorry to hear of Mrs
OL,7,FHayward's passing earlier this year.
OL,8,FWe have since been in contact with the
OL,9,Ffamily, offering the Council's support
OL,10,Fto help them move to suitable
OL,11,Falternative accommodation and
OL,12,Fadditionally delaying the process of
OL,13,Fvacating the property from February to
OL,14,Fallow the family time to grieve and
OL,15,Fexplore other suitable options.
OL,17,F"The offer of Council support to
OL,18,Fexplore other housing options remains."
